the industrial site. The crushing and screening complex is the automated line for production of the fractionated materials. The technological units are provided with the rigid frame constructions. \r\n<br><br>\r\n<strong>The crushing complex</strong> has high automation, high productivity, and high quality production. Either of technological modules is fully individual and can be used as an individual machine for solving other technological tasks. The feeders are needed to take the source material and evenly feed it to the next processing. The crushers grind the material, and then the screens separate it for fractions. Transferring the material from one technological point to other is provided by the belt conveyors.\r\n\r\n<div style="text-align: center;"><img height="1175" width="710" border="0" usemap="#Map" src="/uploads/sheme.jpg"></div><map id="Map" name="Map">  <area href="/Каталог/Щековые-дробилки/18" coords="134,203,208,203,209,181,196,165,214,163,336,165,336,149,525,158,522,125,215,114,210,149,198,149,186,140,171,137,159,152,134,156" shape="poly">  <area href="/Каталог/Конусные-дробилки/21" coords="404,306,410,308,411,305,424,306,426,309,432,307,433,312,435,316,434,319,432,322,531,321,532,336,435,336,435,340,436,344,445,344,446,353,444,356,437,356,434,354,429,357,425,362,414,362,404,355,400,355,400,346,401,338,398,336,402,332" shape="poly">  <area href="/Каталог/Грохота-инерционные" coords="343,481,343,503,357,515,398,486,398,463,367,471,368,447,312,447,311,461,339,461,343,461" shape="poly">  <area href="/Каталог/Грохота-инерционные" coords="440,464,439,486,479,515,493,503,492,481,493,463,531,461,530,446,474,447,476,461,474,476" shape="poly">  <area href="/Каталог/Конусные-дробилки/20" coords="302,675,310,676,314,673,322,673,324,675,331,673,333,678,334,681,333,687,333,690,333,697,336,703,336,706,334,709,336,713,343,713,344,724,338,725,330,724,330,727,326,728,321,729,311,729,307,725,301,722,299,717,302,708,212,711,213,697,302,699,304,697,302,688" shape="poly