/td><td><p>1000</p></td><td><p>1,5</p></td><td><p>210-545</p></td><td><p>0-18</p></td><td><p>11</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n<p>Конвейер ленточный идет в поставку вместе с опорами и площадкой обслуживания.</p>\r\n<p> Мы также производим и поставляем следующие запасные части к конвейерам: ролики опорные и поддерживающие, приводные и натяжные барабаны, и т.д.</p>\r\n<p> Дополнительную информацию Вы можете узнать в отделе маркетинга по телефонам: 247-53-67, 247-53-68, 247-53-69 </p>\r\n', '<p>The belt conveyor is generally used for the continuous transportation of the single-piece, bulk, or lump cargoes in various areas of industry or agriculture, as well as in the machine engineering, food, chemical, metallurgy industries, opencast mining, warehouses, etc.</p>\r\n<p>We sell the belt conveyor and drive. We provide the calculations for the belt conveyor drawing.</p>\r\n<p>The bell conveyor can be used as the individual equipment and in combination with other elements of the technological structure, and this enables to enhance the range of use and the production quantity.</p>\r\n<p>There are simplicity of mechanism, small power consumption, high level of productivity, ability to transfer cargo in horizontal and bevel directions (inclination angle up to 30°); and width of conveyor belt can be 2500 mm. Due to these features the belt conveyor is the basic kind of transportation for various materials.</p>\r\n<p>One of the belt conveyor advantages is the ability to operate not only at the close premises, but in the open territory. The factor, that the belt conveyor can transport cargoes up to some kilometers, enables to adopt the conveyors for the industrial conditions and the particular territory.</p> \r\n<p>The belt conveyor is a construction that contains supports, ring-shaped belt, on which the cargoes are transported, tension and drive rolls, and intermediate bearing rollers.</p> \r\n<p>The belt conveyors are used for transporting the different bulk, single-piece, an